author: @StellaStonhed
text:
Jaehyun who opens with his soft, warm voice, Haechan with his sexy side, Xiaojun who excels as usual. Sungchan fits in so well, I love his voice too. And Ten... Ah Ten... What are you doing to me ? Those high notes are beautiful.
Everyone worked hard and this music remains iconic. Even if there's a disturbing element, let's try to focus on the positive.
I will continue to love and listen to this song. While I understand the disgust and sadness of czennies, please continue to support NCT. I hope you'll be able to appreciate old music again.

author: @bonetrous
text: I loved this song, out of all of NCT's songs released, this was my favorite. It's comforting and everyone's vocals are too good, and most of all i loved it because Taeil's voice. I loved his singing, especially his high note nearing the end. It's so beautiful. But now that man has seriously ruined everything for me. I genuinely can't listen to this song without feeling nauseous and want to throw up. I really hate him for this. I hope they can recreate this song without him. I want to hear more of Ten and Xiaojun instead. I hope everyone deeply affected by him can move on one day...

author: @sj_1341
text:
Esta canción es un temazo!! Me fascinó de principio a fin, y como no, siendo NCT. 
Por una parte no he podido aguantarme las lágrimas al escuchar a my Tennie Ten...soy 10vely desde 2014 y de verdad que verlo crecer más y más con el transcurso del tiempo me hace sentir súper orgullosa de él. Encima ver todos los comentarios positivos sobre él... después de tanta injusticia y dificultades que ha tenido que pasar para poder llegar donde esta... Ten,  lo estas consiguiendo, lo estas haciendo genial. 
Por otra parte, quiero decir que me alegro de haber empezado a stanear NCT desde rookies... haberlos conocido fue una de las mejores cosas que he hecho. Gracias a ellos mis días son mejores y mis oídos son bendecidos con sus temazos, yendo de lo más soft a lo más cañero <3
